usda reject sri lanka 's 80 u.s. dlr wheat price sri lankan food depart offici said the u.s. depart of agricultur reject a u.s. firm ' offer of 80 u.s. dlr per tonn caf to suppli 52,500 tonn of soft wheat to colombo from the pacif northwest . they said sri lanka 's food depart subsequ made a counter-off to five u.s. firm to buy wheat at 85 u.s. dlr caf for april 8-16 deliveri . the compani which obtain usda approv for the propo price must inform the depart befor 1330 gmt , they said .